# MERIT Docker build context
#
# The repository working tree contains multiple historical caches, manuscript
# artifacts, screenshots, and release folders. Docker should package only the
# current UI runtime plus the current v7 precomputed cache needed for local use.

*

!merit-ui-v2/
!merit-ui-v2/api/
!merit-ui-v2/api/**
!merit-ui-v2/merit/
!merit-ui-v2/merit/**
!merit-ui-v2/static/
!merit-ui-v2/static/**
!merit-ui-v2/Logo.png
!merit-ui-v2/README.md
!merit-ui-v2/pyproject.toml
!merit-ui-v2/requirements.txt

!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/
!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/json/
!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/json/**
!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/index.json
!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/study_metadata_index.json
!merit-cache-workbench-full-v7/citation_index.json

!docker/
!docker/**
!docker-compose.merit.yml
